# 🚚 Dropex Vehicle Tracker

A **full-stack Node.js + React application** to **manage and track Dropex vehicle fleet**, enabling:
✅ Vehicle registration  
✅ Tracking KM driven per day  
✅ Fuel consumption monitoring  
✅ Generating QR codes for each vehicle  
✅ Downloadable PDF reports  
✅ Visual chart analytics for PFE presentation

