---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Add, update, and delete vehicles  
✅ Track **KM Today, Litres Consumed, L/100KM**  
✅ Generate **QR Codes** for vehicle details  
✅ Generate **PDF reports** of vehicle data  
✅ View **bar and pie charts** for tracking and fuel efficiency

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose
- **Frontend:** React.js
- **Styling:** CSS (Vanilla) for simplicity
- **PDF & QR:** PDFKit, qrcode
- **Charts:** react-chartjs-2, Chart.js

---

